		            <h2>How to watch the 2026 European Weightlifting Championships live</h2>

		            <p>
			            Official event information is available through the <a href="https://ewf.sport/2026/01/14/2026-ewf-european-championships/" target="_blank">EWF championships page</a>, with live streaming on <a href="https://ewfsport.tv/" target="_blank">EWF TV</a> and live results available via the federation’s official results platform.
		            </p>
		            <p>
